Universial
1. Open Settings
2. Search for Buildnummer
3. Click multiple times on the build nummer, until a message for Developer Options being activated, is shown
4. Exit back to the regular Settings screen
5. Search for Developer Options
6. Look for animations and change to preference (best is 0.5x)
7. Open Limit for Background processes and select a preference

Samsung
1. Open Settings
2. Search for RAM Plus
3. Scroll down and select RAM Plus
4. If you have enough storage, press the highest possible option

Xiaomi
1. Open Settings
2. Search for Memory extension
3. If you have enough storage, press the highest possible option

Xiaomi:
1. Open Settings
2. Search for Performance Mode
3. Press current mode
4. If Battery life isn't a problem, select Performance Mode
